----- 2	Viewing File Contents -------
 
Cmd :- cd ../.. , cat, head, tail

Navigate to home using cd ../.. and then at loc. /etc
Open the content of passwd file using “cat passwd” cmd

-- Head cmd
Here using “head -n 5 passwd” cmd fetch first 5 lines of passwd file
-- Tail cmd
Here using “tail -n 5 passwd” cmd fetch last 5 lines of passwd file

 
---- 3	  Searching for Pattern   -------
Here used “cat passwd | grep root” cmd to display word root in passwd file
 

